article.description: — Dylan Painter had 14 points and 12 rebounds to lift Delaware to a 68-65 win over George Washington on Friday night.
article.headline: Painter leads Delaware over George Washington 68-65
article.linkText: Painter leads Delaware over George Washington 68-65
article.story: NEWARK, Del. -- — Dylan Painter had 14 points and 12 rebounds to lift Delaware to a 68-65 win over George Washington on Friday night. Kevin Anderson had 13 points for Delaware (2-1). Ryan Allen added 12 points. Ebby Asamoah had 10 points. James Bishop had 14 points for the Colonials (1-4). Jamison Battle added 14 points.
